    <h4>What are we?</h4>
    <p>
    It is a platform for organisations to put up the activities they are going to do in a certain area.<br/>
    Users can create their own profiles and look for activities that are happening in their locality.</br/>
    Messaging functionality and location based searching have been incorporated.<br/>
    </p>
